    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey everyone! I\u2019m honestly a bit sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is in absolutely pristine, showroom condition\u2014seriously, not a single scratch or speck of dust! It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, always garage-kept and pampered like a member of the family. It drives like a total dream and still has that wonderful new-car smell. You really won\u2019t find one cleaner than this. Come take a look, I promise you're going to fall in love at first sight!",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
